text: Gakenke: Imiryango 1000 yasizwe iheruheru n’ibiza yashyikirijwe amabati 45000   Yasuwe : 598 Yavuzweho: 0 0   Abo baturage buri muryango wahawe amabati 45 arimo 30 yo gusakaza inzu yo guturamo, 10 yigikoni namabati 5 yubwiherero.  Umuyobozi wa World Vision mu bihugu icyenda byo mu Burasirazuba bwa Afurika, Margaret Schuler, yavuze ko ibiza byishe abaturage abandi bikabasiga iheruheru muri Gakenke nabo byabakoze ku mutima bigatuma batekereza uko babafasha kongera kubaka amazu.  Yagize ati Ibi byabaye nanjye ndi mu Rwanda byaduteye gutekereza icyo twakora ngo tugoboke abantu,ibi ntibihagije ariko tuzakomeza kubatekerezaho tureba icyakorwa ngo bongere bagire ubuzima numutekano usesuye.  Umuyobozi wAkarere ka Gakenke wungirije ushinzwe imibereho myiza,Uwimana Catherine, yashimye iyi nkunga avuga ko hari abaturage bari barasembereye mu baturanyi kandi nyamara bari bafite aho kuba imvura itarabasenyera.  Kugeza abari barasenyewe numvura bamwe bari bacumbikiwe nabaturanyi babo abandi baragondagonze amahema bakingamo umusaya.  Umwe mu basenyewe niriya mvura, Nyabyenda Anaclet yagize ati Nabaga mu gahema nagondagonze, ngiye kugerageza ku buryo imvura izongera kugwa narujuje inzu yo kubamo kuko icyangoraga ni ukubona amabati none arabonetse,ndishimye cyane kandi nabagiraneza ndabashimiye byumwihariko Perezida Paul Kagame kuko ni ikimenyenso cyimiyoborere myiza atugezaho.  Magingo aya hari indi miryango 425 yasenyewe nayo idafite aho yikinga ndetse nabandi basaga 4000 batuye mu manegeka mu Karere ka Gakenke.      bazatsinda@igihe.rw
